Class ParseContext

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.github.syst3ms.skriptparser.parsing.ParseContext

  • public class ParseContext
extends java.lang.Object
    An object that stores data about how an object was parsed. By opposition to MatchContext, this object is immutable.
